      • writeOrNot

        private static corp.everis.pwc.raw.TRANSFORMATION writeOrNot(corp.everis.pwc.raw.TRANSFORMATION t)
        This function will rename the type of the transformation to an incorrect value in case we don't want to print it's details in the console. This is just used for debugging, if we want to be selective in which kind of transformation we want to analyze/output in the console.
        Parameters:
        t - The transformation we want to change it's type from (or leave alone).
        Returns:
        The same transformation with it's type changed (or not).
